{"id": 166, "genre": 1000, "title": "你如何看待星座这回事儿？", "description": "《纽约时报》星座专栏的苏珊大妈病倒了，她的星座运程晚了几天刊出，结果招致了Facebook上很多人的攻击，因为星座运程晚到，他们都不晓得如何生活了！\r\n", "record_count": 2967, "comment_count": 45, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160608143539emz8oNv20rRnGLk1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-11-28T08:51:47Z", "questions": [{"id": 135, "title": "你如何看待星座这回事儿？", "content": "你如何看待星座这回事儿？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 1140, "content": "我完全不信星座的", "image": "img/option/option/20160608143247hGDp7RJY1OaMF8um.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1141, "content": "我为了追女孩儿有时候装作信", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192604Do8AKuPjv3dVMJi6.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1142, "content": "我大概知道12星座，但总分不清", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194015G9uk15WtTf8jsoBH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1143, "content": "我通常只信星座运势中自己想信的部分", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194008QWDL62F9GR3sr1Bi.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1144, "content": "我会做大事儿之前看看星座运势", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192604G3DQ15OJZYS6ATbR.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1145, "content": "我不仅知道自己的星座，还知道自己的上升星座", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192604TXM2zPa76kHRSsyV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1146, "content": "我很信星座，会完全按照运程做事", "image": "img/option/option/201606071926045XRwSpCfOdezPtyY.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1147, "content": "我会判断别人星座or看星盘", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192604q4BZnOwiYM1umWTE.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}